---------------------------------
Installation (on Debian/Ubuntu)
---------------------------------

1. Pidgin
==========

Download and extract the newest pidgin source

# aptitude install libgkt2.0-dev libgstreamer0.10-dev libgtkspell-dev
libxml-perl libdbus-glib-1-dev g libgnutls-dev !!!!ADD_OTHER_USEFULL_LIBS!!!!

$ cd pidgin-*
$ ./configure
$ make
# make install

run pidgin

To see debug messages run pidgin like that:

pidgin -d | grep one_time_pad


2. Pidgin-Paranoia
===================

Get it from svn:
$ svn co https://pidgin-paranoia.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/pidgin-paranoia/trunk pidgin-paranoia

$ cd pidgin-paranoia
$ ./autogen.sh
$ ./configure
$ make
# make install

Done. Activate it in the pidgin plug-in menu.


uninstall: (who wants to do that anyway? ;) )
$ cd pidgin-paranoia
# make uninstall


